App
 [x] Unknown route should return 404
 [x] Debug should return environment
 [x] Get resource should return all resources
 [x] Get resource by id should return only one resource
 [x] Get resource by invalid id should return 404
 [x] Create resource with no input should return 400
 [x] Create resource with missing input should return 400
 [x] Create resource with valid input should return 201
 [x] Update resource with no input should return 400
 [x] Update resource with invalid id should return 404
 [x] Update resource with valid request should return 204 and update resource
 [x] Delete resource with invalid id should return 404
 [x] Delete resource with valid id should return 204 and delete resource

